HOVER HIKER
by Ridgemont Outfitters on Apr 01, 2016




At Ridgemont we’re committed to making the great outdoors accessible to even very lazy people, so we’ve developed the Hover Hiker…
Oh man, this is starting to feel a bit too real.
APRIL FOOLS!
Although, we’re pretty surprised this doesn’t already exist, we hope it never does. Keep on hiking!



