  Outback II – Ridgemont Outfitters
  




























































Ridgemont Shop / Outback II








Footwear

Heritage
Outback II x Iron and Resin
Monty Hi
Monty Lo
Outback II
Mesa II
Crest
Women's




Apparel

T-Shirts

Accessories

Socks
Hats
Bottles

Sale

CLEARANCE




















 
The Ridgemont Outback II is our most versatile style. Constructed of durable 2mm waxed full grain leather, waxed cotton canvas, a bespoke open cell insole and a hi-density 100% rubber, lugged vulcanized outsole, it's designed to stand up to all but the most extreme environments.  NEW for this version is a lockstitch side seam for an ultra secure outsole bond and a BiFit composite lasting board for enhanced durability, comfort and improved flex in the forefoot.  In addition each colour has a full DWR (durable water repellent) coating so any moisture just beads off the leather.
Unlike most other hiking boots, it's not so bulky that you'll look like you just got finished hiking the Muir trail if you feel like grabbing some breakfast after your morning hike. Outside magazine said 'This Boot Can Do Anything!'. We tend to agree!
Plus it's now available down to a men's size US5 for the younger hikers and also the fairer ones..
 
 






  
 



