Company Profile
ASK  QUESTION







“When we couldn’t find the perfect adventure footwear for people like us, we set out to design it ourselves.  Ridgemont is all about form and function.  It's great quality, good looking footwear that performs when you're walking the dog or conquering the trail—but also feels comfortable enough to wear at work or out for dinner. We combine the best materials and construction techniques but with a modern aesthetic. Our mission is to move the outdoor footwear market forward to the 21st century.



Alex Hall
CEO, Ridgemont Outfitters




Key Facts

100% revenue growth year on year
56k visitors to website in last 12 months up 50% on previous 12 months
Founders started three other apparel and athletic brands prior to Ridgemont
Website converts 4% of visitors
Now offering worldwide delivery to Japan, Australia, Europe & South America

Our Ambition
Ridgemont appeals to all - the traditional outdoorsman - the casual trail hiker - the fashion conscious individual.  Our ambition is to continue to offer stylish footwear that incorporates the latest technical innovations.  By selling direct to consumers we have had the flexibility to introduce new styles and designs frequently and respond to feedback and stay ahead of the curve. As we grow we will make our products more widely available through national retailers to fuel continued growth.
