Why I Like Ridgemont Outfitters



When I consider an investment, my criteria is not just investing in a great idea, but also the leadership I am investing in. In Ridgemont, not only is it a great product and innovative concept, the founders Alex & Stacy have the combined knowledge, experience and passion to make Ridgemont a success and a global brand. In the first two years Ridgemont has already challenged the traditional outdoor footwear market and has established itself as a truly viable alternative. Ridgemont now has a good direct to consumer revenue stream and through these channels it is positioned well to continue to grow quickly. Simply, I bet on Ridgemont and Alex and Stacy because I believe in the product and concept, and that the founders are the right executive team to make it a huge success.



Martin Hepworth

